  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/c47064788a44a62446a6b9821fcc9130.poster.avif?t=1732202208\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/c47064788a44a62446a6b9821fcc9130.webm?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/c47064788a44a62446a6b9821fcc9130.mp4?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Magic Kaleidoscope is an amazing anti-stress coloring game</strong> </h2>  where you can become the creator of your own magical textures and animations. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/5523628b74c416881d589392433bee5d.poster.avif?t=1732202208\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/5523628b74c416881d589392433bee5d.webm?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/5523628b74c416881d589392433bee5d.mp4?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Mathematical formulas and fractals breathe life into a unique animated library of materials, creating magnificent and vibrant pictures. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/77f2c0ee2db06c91fb3aae73313ea69f.poster.avif?t=1732202208\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/77f2c0ee2db06c91fb3aae73313ea69f.webm?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/77f2c0ee2db06c91fb3aae73313ea69f.mp4?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Customize your settings, play with colors, sizes, and animation speed to make each of your creations unique and one-of-a-kind.<br><br>Moreover, you can share your masterpieces with friends! <br><br>Just copy the code, send it to your friend, and they can enjoy your magical kaleidoscope.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/46d51d56da00038e8f6dfb5a0caa74cb.poster.avif?t=1732202208\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/46d51d56da00038e8f6dfb5a0caa74cb.webm?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/46d51d56da00038e8f6dfb5a0caa74cb.mp4?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can also use the results of your experiments as a background in videos, create unique avatars, or set up a festive atmosphere using a projector.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/ee27cc8e5d415352068e2634383aef2e.poster.avif?t=1732202208\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/ee27cc8e5d415352068e2634383aef2e.webm?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/ee27cc8e5d415352068e2634383aef2e.mp4?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Magic Kaleidoscope is art, imagination development, and an engaging way to relieve stress for both children and adults. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/1c229019d9a34ce1bc35b0a779ee6e36.poster.avif?t=1732202208\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/1c229019d9a34ce1bc35b0a779ee6e36.webm?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/1c229019d9a34ce1bc35b0a779ee6e36.mp4?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Forget about everyday problems and dive into an endless ocean of colors and shapes!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/a5e3e1e46f6dcf6d365bb7253edb93b4.poster.avif?t=1732202208\" width=620 height=88 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/a5e3e1e46f6dcf6d365bb7253edb93b4.webm?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/a5e3e1e46f6dcf6d365bb7253edb93b4.mp4?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/c47064788a44a62446a6b9821fcc9130.poster.avif?t=1732202208\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/c47064788a44a62446a6b9821fcc9130.webm?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/c47064788a44a62446a6b9821fcc9130.mp4?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Magic Kaleidoscope is an amazing anti-stress coloring game</strong> </h2>  where you can become the creator of your own magical textures and animations. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/5523628b74c416881d589392433bee5d.poster.avif?t=1732202208\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/5523628b74c416881d589392433bee5d.webm?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/5523628b74c416881d589392433bee5d.mp4?t=1732202208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Mathematical formulas and fractals breathe life into a unique animated library of materials, creating magnificent and vibrant pictures. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/77f2c0ee2db06c91fb3aae73313ea69f.poster.avif?t=1732202208\" width=620 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449130/extras/77f2c0ee2db06c91fb3aae73313ea69f.webm?